---
import { Icon } from "astro-iconify";

import Card from "./Card.astro";
import CardHeading from "./CardHeading.astro";
---

<div class="card-container">
  <Card link="/posts/what-is-a-bike-grid" notarget>
    <Icon name="material-symbols:grid-on" class="icon" />
    <CardHeading>What's a Bike Grid?</CardHeading>
    <p>10% of streets. 10mph. Protected. All across Chicago.</p>
  </Card>

  <Card notarget link="/posts/CBGN-direct-action-101">
    <Icon name="material-symbols:edit-road-outline-rounded" class="icon" />
    <CardHeading>Why do we Jam?</CardHeading>
    <p>Advocacy is good, but it's not cutting it. Read more here.</p>
  </Card>

  <Card link="/about" notarget>
    <Icon name="material-symbols:signpost-outline-rounded" class="icon" />
    <CardHeading>About us</CardHeading>
    <p>
      We're a grassroots group of Chicagoans who want to see safer streets.
      Learn more about the current organizers.
    </p>
  </Card>

  <Card link="https://www.gofundme.com/f/flags-and-flyers-for-bike-grid-now">
    <Icon name="material-symbols:savings-outline-rounded" class="icon" />
    <CardHeading>Support Us</CardHeading>
    <p>
      We'd love your support through gofundme so we can keep printing flyers,
      stickers, etc. Reach out on Social Media if you'd like some stickers!
    </p>
  </Card>
</div>

<style>
  .card-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    grid-gap: calc(5 * var(--space));
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
  }

  .icon {
    width: calc(16 * var(--space));
    height: calc(16 * var(--space));
  }

  @media only screen and (max-width: 800px) {
    .card-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
